  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIf you remove/add the user from the group chat, the system message that the user left/added the group will be displayed only after the app restart\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Create a private group chat\r\n2. Remove/add one of the members\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe system message that [user] left the group/was added is present\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe system message that [user] left the group/ was added is absent\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/117639195/225014837-d43b7056-034c-48ce-80cf-8fff8e398035.mov\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n \r\n- Status desktop version: 0.10.0-rc13\r\n- Operating System: macos\r\n\r\nTODO: it would be nice to resolve, when user left the group and when user was removed by admin from the group\r\n\r\n",
